node.text: Jetstream Blue is such an underrated color😍💙 12 DAYS LEFT to WIN This 700HP Z06!!!🇺🇸 Freshly built heads/cam package from @completestreet making 601WHP! 2008, 38,000 miles, clean title🙌 Every $5 spent on inshanedesigns.com gets you 15🎟 Entries! Good luck! Pic by @alexthespangler 📸

node.text: 7107 miles in the @ramtrucks TRX😈 She’s been on the beach, on a boat, on an island, the top of the imogene pass, and up the pa turnpike more times than I can count. An offroader, a 1,000hp Corvette tow rig, a dog ambulance, and a daily driver. We’re just getting started😎I wouldn’t choose any other truck on the market right now-🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸

node.text: NEW VIDEO IS LIVE!!!🔥 revealing the new vehicle that nobody could guess!😂 (Well like 2 of you guessed it but basically nobody😂) We also take delivery of the freshly built 700HP Z06 and I get my first ride in a plaid tesla🤯🤯🤯 Holy shit I’m a believer now😭 Don’t miss it!

node.text: The Z06 is BACK from @completestreet and its so fucking awesome😂😂😂 Forgot how much fun a fast manual car is!😍 Andrew (Owner of @completestreet ) Also took me out in his new Tesla Model S Plaid and HOLY SHIT...
